  "explanation": [
    "Property: $|adj A| = |A|^{n-1}$. Here n=2.",
    "$|B| = |adj A| = |A|^{2-1} = |A| = 2$.",
    "Det of B: $1(\\alpha) - 3(1) = \\alpha - 3$.",
    "$\\alpha - 3 = 2 \\Rightarrow \\alpha = 5$."
